snippet.title: Game Showcase - Nakoruru: Anohito Kara no Okurimono (Dreamcast)
snippet.description: Nakoruru: Anohito Kara no Okurimono (ナコルル 〜あのひとからのおくりもの〜 ) is an adventure game for the Sega Dreamcast. It is a spinoff of SNK's Samurai Shodown series.
